title: Tidal Wave of Darkness - Berserk Vol. 20 [Part 2] & Vol. 21 [Part 1]
description:
Let's talk about the Conviction Arc of #Berserk!
This video covers Deluxe Edition 7 - Vol. 20 [Part 2] & Vol. 21 [Part 1], which includes the chapters:
"Collapse" and "Shadows of Idea 1-3" as well as "Leaping Fish", "Bestial Priest 1-2", "Those Who Cling, Those Who Struggle", "Tidal Wave of Darkness 1-2", "Resonance", and "The Sky Fall".
